description:
[MV] Kwon Jin Ah(권진아) _ Tell me about your day(오늘 뭐 했는지 말해봐)

*English subtitles are now available. :D
(Please click on 'CC' button or activate 'Interactive Transcript' function)

[Notice] 1theK YouTube is also an official channel for the MV, and music shows will count the views from this channel too.

Kwon Jin Ah asks the person who has always been watching my ‘today’ near me in a lonely and moist voice. It is a song to ask the person, saying “tell me what you did today because I want to hear your voice” like venting the tangled feelings of the day, one day after a long time. The strong loneliness that anyone can feel touches your heart. The voice of Kwon Jin Ah who sang about the loneliness, which can be called selfish, is sad and cold.
